7.2 Projects without a NEXT item
================================

If a project has active tasks but none are marked NEXT, this usually
indicates:
  1. Missing dependency configuration (no ‘ORG_GTD_FIRST_TASKS’
     property)
  2. org-edna is not enabled
  3. Dependency properties need recalculation

   *Solution*: Put the point on the project heading and run ‘M-x
org-gtd-projects-fix-todo-keywords-for-project-at-point’.

   *Note*: Make sure org-edna is enabled: ‘(org-edna-mode 1)’ in your
init file.  See *note Configuring:: for setup instructions.

   See also: *note Working with Projects (Advanced):: for complete
project troubleshooting guide.


