7.4.1 Keywords not working
--------------------------

If TODO keywords aren't changing correctly:

  1. *Check ‘org-todo-keywords’ includes all GTD keywords in one
     sequence*:
          (setq org-todo-keywords
                '((sequence "TODO" "NEXT" "WAIT" "|" "DONE" "CNCL")))

