          (setq org-gtd-keyword-mapping
                '((todo . "TODO")
                  (next . "NEXT")
                  (wait . "WAIT")
                  (canceled . "CNCL")))

  3. *Remove any ‘#+TODO:’ lines from GTD org files*

   See *note Configuring:: for complete setup instructions.


